$templateCache.put("views/en/cookie_app_en.html","<update-meta name=robots content=\"noindex, nofollow\"></update-meta><div class=other-pages-container><div class=wrapper><h1>Tikkie cookie?</h1><p>The Tikkie app uses cookies and similar techniques (all referred to as \'cookies\') to make our service more personal and user-friendly.</p><br><p>You decide which cookies you want us to place on your device. We think the <b>Personal</b> option gives you the best user experience.</p><h3>Here\'s your cookie choice:</h3><div class=cookie-box><div class=list><table><tr><th></th><th>Personal üíÅ‚Äçüç™</th></tr><tr><td><span class=green><img ng-src={{iconCheck}} class=height10></span></td><td>Cookies for advertisements and relevant offers for our products and services.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=green><img ng-src={{iconCheck}} class=height10></span></td><td>Cookies for advertisements and relevant offers for our products and services, including on third party websites.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=green><img ng-src={{iconCheck}} class=height10></span></td><td>Functional and analytical cookies (see below).</td></tr></table></div></div><div class=cookie-box><div class=list><table><tr><th></th><th>Functional ‚öôÔ∏èüç™</th></tr><tr><td><span class=green><img ng-src={{iconCheck}} class=height10></span></td><td>Functional cookies, which optimise the Tikkie app‚Äôs performance.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=green><img ng-src={{iconCheck}} class=height10></span></td><td>Analytical cookies, which track visits to our app.</td></tr></table></div></div><v-accordion class=vAccordion--default><v-pane ng-repeat=\"pane in items\" ng-if=\"pane.category == \'Veiligheid\'\"><v-pane-header><b>{{ ::pane.header }}</b></v-pane-header><v-pane-content><div ng-bind-html=pane.content></div></v-pane-content></v-pane><v-pane><v-pane-header><b>Why have cookies?</b></v-pane-header><v-pane-content>We use cookies to analyse the use of the Tikkie app, to enable to share content through social media and to align content and advertisements with your preferences. These cookies are also placed by third parties.<br><br>If you click \'I accept\' in the selection screen, we\'ll place advertising, social media, functional and analytical cookies. If you click \'I don\'t accept\' we\'ll only place functional and analytical cookies, which simply allow the app to work properly and to analyse data. This data is gathered anonymously.<br><br>Want to know more about what a cookie is and does? It\'s all in the <a class=exampleLink href=\"/privacy/en/v1/\">privacy statement</a>.</v-pane-content></v-pane></v-accordion><br><br></div></div>");
